summary: This is a Palm Beach Police Department property receipt form, used to document items taken into custody. The form is blank, indicating it is a template or unused form, not a completed record of specific property seized in the Epstein case.
keyFacts: The document is a blank Palm Beach Police Department property receipt form (Form *52).
It is a template for documenting property that is found, deceased, personal, confiscated, evidence, etc.
The form includes fields for incident number, date, property details, owner information, and suspect information.
No specific persons, property, or incidents are detailed on this form.
The document is part of the Epstein case files but contains no case-specific data.
